{
  "stem": "26983.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 53.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We marched out of the camp, in five-- always, everything five.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was always five people, in a row of five.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we children were with the very first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Separately.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember because we were in the block of men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived-- we went first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went somewhere on a-- out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were some factory or something on the right side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, because I was the very first one and the SS man was a little behind usm somehow we went in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a big [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I looked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a tiny, little window on the side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was just looking around-- what it is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he said, raus, raus!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We should go out, and we should go some other way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was the gas chamber of crematorium number 4, which later on, I visited several times.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But at that time I didn't know it, what it is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because, uh--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The road went there, and we had to go in another way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the first group went into it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said raus, raus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I could see it exactly how it looked, and with these windows, and so on-- these small windows on the top.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went further on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came to a huge place, which was called sauna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't had idea what is sauna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later, we knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's-- in Finnish or so, it means washing hall, a special-- Area, yes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--area.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But our transport had special treatment that we only, of course, knew later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Usually, if a transport came, maybe we are the only-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] Tell it to you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So let's say I have a transport of 2,000 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were 2,500.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were two groups of 2,500 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
